Scattershot/Nemesis Enforcer/Serpentor:




The trio burst out into booming laughter as they saw Diskus bounce around.

Scattershot fired off another twenty-five rounds at Diskus, still laughing.

Nemesis Enforcer fired off twenty-five rapid laser blasts at Diskus, 
remembering their was a trash compactor that could fit the stasis locked 
robot inside the base.

Serpentor fired another blast from his plasma charge at Diskus torso, his 
weapon running low on energy.
